    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Huntin' Season Begins</strong></h2><br>When the world becomes over-run by ducks and other phenomenon, there's only one man who can stop them. You play as the professional hunter, &quot;Ed&quot; as he goes on his mission to cut down the duck population. Along the hunt you will come across &quot;encounters&quot; such as aliens, zombies, and clowns.  Choose from a variety of items and find the perfect combination to help stop the overabundance of ducks.  Combo the fancy duck to increase the power of all the items you currently have equipped.  As your journey continues the duck population will continue to explode until you are overrun.  How long can you survive?<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Variety of items to choose from consisting of attack, defense, and utility.</li><li>Combo system increases power of items as the combo rises.</li><li>Many unique encounters whose purpose is to stop you from huntin'.</li><li>Endless, so your journey of huntin' ducks isn't over until you are finally overrun.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055200/extras/49f28275bf3c1f156f8a461bc7e2e73d.poster.avif?t=1722600780\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055200/extras/49f28275bf3c1f156f8a461bc7e2e73d.webm?t=1722600780\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3055200/extras/49f28275bf3c1f156f8a461bc7e2e73d.mp4?t=1722600780\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
